  "description": "Why do some of us see change as an opportunity while others see it as a threat? Every major inflection in human history has left some people behind. Follow Shey Sinope as he fights to discover who is to blame when he falls victim to the AI revolution. In the process, you will discover a personal roadmap to keep your professional skills relevant, vibrant, and in demand and emerge entertained, amused, but - more importantly - far better equipped to ensure your career is future ready! Drs Schuster &amp; Oxley are long-time collaborators and former work colleagues. Their award-winning writing partnership was founded on a mission to reimagine career and professional advice books for a modern audience. They say their goal is to entertain while helping at least one person better navigate a difficult career challenge… they hope that person is you. Read more",
